1.	Create a spring boot application. 

2.	Add the following dependency for validation from maven repository
	<dependency>
    	<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    	<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-validation</artifactId>
	</dependency>
	
3.	create a package validation

4.	Inside the package create an annotation (ValidAadharCard) in the same way as 
	we create classes and interfaces. Notice that annotation is an interface 
	with @ symbol

5.	Create the validator class (FourteenDigitValidator) implements ConstraintValidator

6.	Create a model class to use the custom annotation

	